Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Petrol shortage in US
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bxq4
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 20 May 1979
Nationwide petrol shortage blamed on US oil companies. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less